title: 4K - The Night of the Eldritch Beasts 1959 - Your skin will crawl with fear - Horror SciFi

sources.title: 4K - The Night of the Eldritch Beasts 1959 - Your skin will crawl with fear - Horror SciFi
sources.description:
On Dr. Marlowe's isolated island, Captain Thorne and Rook dock, only to find the Doctor's mutated shrew experiments have overgrown into ravenous, oversized terrors besieging the lab. Trapped with Jerry, Griswold, and Radford, Thorne must outsmart these furry fiends using improvised armor and a barrel-based escape plan before they all end up as shrew-d appetizers.

Original title: The Killer Shrews / The Attack of the Killer Shrews (1959) 
Directed by Ray Kellogg. Written by Ken Curtis.

Main cast:
James Best — Captain Thorne Sherman
Ingrid Goude — Ann Craigis
Ken Curtis — Jerry Farrell
Gordon McLendon — Dr. Radford Baines
Baruch Lumet — Dr. Marlowe Craigis
"Judge" Henry Dupree - Rook Griswold
Alfred DeSoto - Mario


Black & White version: https://youtu.be/C5CwIBLVXQE
